""SELECT t.\"FarmId\", (

    FROM \"TillagePrograms\" AS t0

    WHERE t0.\"FarmId\" = @__farmId_0 AND t0.\"IsActive\" AND t.\"FarmId\" = t0.\"FarmId\"

    FROM \"TillageServices\" AS t1
    WHERE t.\"Id\" = t1.\"TillageProgramId\")), 0)::int AS \"TotalServices\", COALESCE(sum((

    FROM \"TillageServices\" AS t2

    LIMIT 1) AS \"FarmName\", COALESCE(sum(t.\"TotalHectares\"), 0) AS \"TotalPlanned\", COALESCE(sum(t.\"TilledHectares\"), 0) AS \"TotalTilled\", COALESCE(sum((
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM \"TillageServices\" AS t1
    WHERE t.\"Id\" = t1.\"TillageProgramId\")), 0)::int AS \"TotalServices\", COALESCE(sum((
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM \"TillageServices\" AS t2
    WHERE t.\"Id\" = t2.\"TillageProgramId\" AND t2.\"IsCompleted\")), 0)::int AS \"CompletedServices\", COALESCE(sum((
    SELECT COALESCE(sum(COALESCE(t3.\"ServiceCost\", 0.0)), 0.0)
    FROM \"TillageServices\" AS t3
    WHERE t.\"Id\" = t3.\"TillageProgramId\")), 0.0) AS \"TotalRevenue\"
FROM \"TillagePrograms\" AS t
WHERE t.\"FarmId\" = @__farmId_0 AND t.\"IsActive\"
GROUP BY t.\"FarmId\"
LIMIT 1"

""SELECT f.\"Name\", f.\"Address\", f.\"ContactPerson\", f.\"PhoneNumber\", f.\"Email\", f.\"Description\", f.\"Vision\", f.\"Mission\", f.\"Website\", f.\"Year\", f.\"FoundingMembers\", f.\"KeyMilestones\", f.\"Size\", f.\"Arable\", f.\"Cleared\", f.\"Terrain\", f.\"Latitude\", f.\"Longitude\", f.\"Elevation\", f.\"PastCrops\", f.\"LandManagementPractice\", f.\"SecurityMeasures\", f.\"WaterSource\", f.\"WaterAvailability\", f.\"Irrigated\", f.\"Equipment\", f.\"SoilType\", f.\"RoadAccess\", f.\"Problems\", f.\"Personnel\", f.\"Recommendations\", f.\"WardId\", f.\"LocalAuthorityId\", f.\"DistrictId\", f.\"ProvinceId\", f.\"Region\", f.\"Conference\", f.\"CommunityPrograms\", f.\"Partnerships\", f.\"Classrooms\", f.\"Laboratories\", f.\"SportsFacilities\", f.\"Library\", f.\"AverageExamScores\", f.\"ExtraCurricularAchievements\", f.\"MaleTeachers\", f.\"FemaleTeachers\", f.\"MaleStudents\", f.\"FemaleStudents\", f.\"StudentDemographics\", f.\"DayScholars\", f.\"BoardingScholars\", f.\"NonTeachingStaff\", f.\"Buildings\", w.\"Name\" AS \"Ward\", l.\"Name\" AS \"LocalAuthority\", d.\"Name\" AS \"District\", p.\"Name\" AS \"Province\", f.\"Id\", f.\"UpdatedAt\", f.\"Deleted\", f.\"CreatedDate\", f.\"CreatorId\", f.\"ModifiedBy\", f.\"IsArchived\", f.\"IsActive\"
FROM \"Farms\" AS f
LEFT JOIN \"Wards\" AS w ON f.\"WardId\" = w.\"Id\"
LEFT JOIN \"LocalAuthorities\" AS l ON f.\"LocalAuthorityId\" = l.\"Id\"
LEFT JOIN \"Districts\" AS d ON f.\"DistrictId\" = d.\"Id\"
